<main class="dashboard-container">
    <div class="welcome-banner">
        <h1>Welcome, Head of Examination Department!</h1>
        <ul>
            <li>Receive and manage assigned tasks for exam review and approval.</li>
            <li>Assign exam review/feedback tasks to lecturers.</li>
            <li>Review, approve, and update exams based on feedback and progress.</li>
            <li>Receive notifications about exam progress and updates.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</main>